sentences: Jonathan Allan "Jody" Stecher (born  June 1, 1946) is an American singer and musician.
Jonathan Allan Stecher was born on June 1, 1946, in Brooklyn, New York.
He has collaborated with Krishna Bhatt on an unusual album of fusion music, Rasa (1982).
He met Kate Brislin (a former member of Any Old Time String Band) in 1974, and they started performing actively as a duo in 1985; they married on 29 July 1987.
